SUMMARY:[Federal Maine-Related] Notice of Intent To Prepare an Environment
 al Impact Statement\, Washington County\, Maine
DESCRIPTION:FHWA\, on behalf of the Maine Department of Transportation (Ma
 ineDOT)\, is issuing this notice to advise the public that an Environmenta
 l Impact Statement (EIS) will be prepared for proposed transportation impr
 ovements to the Machias Dike Bridge (#2246) on U.S. Route 1 in Machias\, M
 aine. The bridge consists of four box culverts with tide gates. MaineDOT i
 nvites the public to provide input on the purpose and need and range of al
 ternatives to be considered\, and to identify environmental impacts or iss
 ues related to the project.\nhttps://www.federalregister.gov/documents/202
 6/07/09/2026-13876/notice-of-intent-to-prepare-an-environmental-impact-sta
 tement-washington-county-maine
